{"tid":1478744,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我地係中小企老闆有野想同大家講","createTime":"2019-08-16T15:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:54:41.000Z","uid":16184,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5387a016901a70a22e7645368020d844bb1ba385","tid":1478744,"uid":16184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:42:22.000Z","msg":"[size=4]因為你地示威，真係令到好多中小企百上加斤，本身租已經好撚貴，持續抗爭令到好多鋪頭冇生意，一個星期內更有2日無得開工，好似我鋪頭係油尖旺區，就更加係重災區。<br />\n小弟既職業比較特殊，本身諗住對自己冇咩影響，風平浪靜果時每個月都有最少50-60k月入，而家搞到得返15-25k一個月，由6月到今日，一日差過一日。好多一樣做生意既朋友，都話就快頂唔住，好想快d完！[/size=4］<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但我地都唔會割蓆，就算鋪頭執粒，每個月得1皮野，我都會繼續支持抗爭運動！香港得一個，生意冇左再做過！我都算係社運老鬼，2014開始到今日都依然同大家一齊發夢，一路都冇放棄過香港，就算而家我畢左業自已做生意，我都唔會放棄，我地一班中小企既老闆都會繼續支持大家！你地即管去做你地認為岩既野，唔好比自已有後悔既機會！你地要記住好多人支持你地，好似我同朋友咁都有幫手，你地做緊一件好正確既事，要繼續一齊抗落去！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2df2d43b74ece3ecc4d5c4c79be419999e7ba3","tid":1478744,"uid":160991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:43:39.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f750d144df67c83a05a6eff1d661e5fc14897cdf","tid":1478744,"uid":268538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:44:15.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec01e199cbab206e20cdf21ccbbb1d389df5555b","tid":1478744,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EXxPBQ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2